# Alert Definitions & SLO Management - 2025

Define Service Level Indicators (SLIs), Service Level Objectives (SLOs), and actionable alerts with proper thresholds and escalation.

**Justification:** Well-defined alerts prevent alert fatigue, ensure critical issues are addressed quickly, and maintain service reliability.

## 🎯 Single Responsibility
This rule ONLY defines WHAT to alert on and WHEN. Not how to respond (see incident-management) or how to visualize (see dashboards).

